Key Features
Visual Design:
Sharingan Pulse: Header icon with rhythmic animation
Type Color Coding: Panels (crimson), Pages (dark red), Chapters (orange), Bubbles (gold)
EMS Hover Effects: Left border glow, horizontal slide, thumbnail brightness
Expanded View: Side-by-side original/translated comparison with "EMS" red text glow
Functionality:
Smart Filtering: All/Panel/Page/Chapter tabs with instant filtering
Privacy-First: 7-day auto-delete, local storage only, explicit privacy notice
Quick Actions: Retranslate, copy text, go to page, delete with confirmation
Duplicate Prevention: Same URL+text combinations are deduplicated
Time Intelligence: "Just now", "5m ago", "2h ago" formatting
Data Management:
Deduplication: Prevents history spam from re-reading same panels
Auto-Cleanup: Hourly purge of entries >7 days old
Size Limits: Maximum 10 items (configurable)
Rich Metadata: Manga title, chapter, page numbers, language pairs
Events:
historyupdate - Add/delete/clear operations
itemexpand - User expands detail view
retranslate - Request to retranslate specific item


Integration:

<recent-history id="history"></recent-history>
<script>
  const history = document.getElementById('history');
  
  // Add new translation
  history.addEntry({
    type: 'panel',
    title: 'Speech bubble text...',
    originalText: '元気ですか？',
    translatedText: 'How are you?',
    mangaTitle: 'Naruto',
    chapterNum: 1,
    pageNum: 5,
    sourceUrl: 'https://mangadex.org/chapter/...',
    thumbnail: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,...'
  });
  
  // Listen for retranslate requests
  history.addEventListener('retranslate', (e) => {
    console.log('Retranslate:', e.detail);
  });
</script>